WEBVTT

00:07:59.080 --> 00:08:01.376
the director of a free clinic

00:08:01.400 --> 00:08:04.880
primarily serving
the uninsured in Arkansas.

00:08:05.720 --> 00:08:09.096
Monika loves telling me that the doctors,

00:08:09.120 --> 00:08:11.656
who volunteer at her free clinic

00:08:11.680 --> 00:08:13.976
routinely tell her

00:08:14.000 --> 00:08:18.280
that they've never worked
in such a beautiful, light-filled place.

00:08:19.320 --> 00:08:20.936
Monika believes

00:08:20.960 --> 00:08:23.016
that even people experiencing poverty

00:08:23.040 --> 00:08:25.536
deserve quality health care.

00:08:25.560 --> 00:08:26.856
And what's more,

00:08:26.880 --> 00:08:30.296
she believes they deserve
to receive that care